@startuml state_charging_session
!theme plain
title ChargingSession State Machine\n(Sommerville Ch.5)

[*] --> Active : Kullanici QR tarar ve sarj baslatir (REQ 1.21)\n/ startBatteryLevel kaydedilir\n/ gercek zamanli takip baslar

Active --> Completed : Kullanici "Tamamla" butonuna basar\n/ endBatteryLevel kaydedilir\n/ energyConsumed hesaplanir\n/ totalCost = energyConsumed * pricingPerKWh\n/ cuzdandan otomatik odeme\n/ DigitalReceipt olusturulur
Active --> Completed : 2 saat siniri doldu (REQ 1.9)\n/ otomatik tamamlama\n/ bildirim gonderilir

state Active #FFD700 {
  state "Monitoring" as mon
  mon : Polling (her 5 saniye)
  mon : current kWh, estimated time, cost so far
  mon : Frontend: Analogue (progress bar) + Digital (kWh/TL)
}

state Completed #90EE90

note right of Completed
  Tamamlandiginda:
  1. energyConsumed hesaplanir (kWh)
  2. totalCost = energyConsumed * pricingPerKWh
  3. Wallet'tan otomatik dusulur (Transaction olusur)
  4. Bakiye <50 TL ise bildirim (REQ 1.15)
  5. DigitalReceipt olusturulur
  6. Charger status -> available
  7. Reservation status -> completed
  8. Notification gonderilir
  9. Kullanici makbuzu goruntuleyebilir (REQ 1.20)
end note

@enduml
